N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 206.8 - Fee for copies

State Regulations

The fee for copies of records is hereby fixed at 25 cents for
each page or portion of a page measuring up to 9 inches by 14
inches. Notes
